(73, 28, '<p>Задание первое исправления:</p>\r\n<p>Код форматировал</p>\r\n<p>Ссылку из галереи на главную добавил</p>\r\n<p>На странице \"Про меня\" исправил ссылку на главную</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #363636; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Порушена структура навігаційного меню на деяких сторінках. Навігація на кожній сторінці повинна бути однакова (Исправил)</span></p>', 'https://www.dropbox.com/s/chu06e5e5f9t2uf/Week1_season3_Mikhov_correction.zip?dl=0', 0, '2017-03-23 20:58:26', '2017-03-24 13:06:39', 12, '0'),
(74, 12, '<p>Проверка ДЗ говорят не отправляется</p>', '', 0, '2017-03-24 03:54:37', '2017-04-26 15:30:49', 13, '0'),
(75, 20, '<p>Відповіді на ДЗ</p>\r\n<p>1 border</p>\r\n<p>2 padding</p>\r\n<p>3 background</p>\r\n<p>4 box-shadow</p>\r\n<p>5 background-repeat</p>\r\n<p>6 border-left-color</p>\r\n<p>Test</p>\r\n<p>1 Зробив помилку в 9 питанні (не зрозумів суті питання вибрав a:visited)</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'https://www.dropbox.com/s/smyklxnli0m0a35/dz.7z?dl=0', 0, '2017-03-24 04:05:39', '2017-03-24 14:24:58', 14, '0'),
(76, 12, '<p>dd</p>', 'd', 0, '2017-03-24 04:36:03', '2017-04-26 15:30:49', 13, '0'),
(77, 26, '<p>1. border;</p>\r\n<p>2. padding;</p>\r\n<p>3. background;</p>\r\n<p>4. text-shadow, но я так понял, что только для текста, а для блоков box-shadow;</p>\r\n<p>5. background-repeat;</p>\r\n<p>6. border-right-color;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>ошибки в вопросах теста: 2, 3, 6, 11, 12, 15((((.</p>', 'https://www.dropbox.com/s/2hkq72hon0yffmv/dz.zip?dl=0', 0, '2017-03-24 05:51:44', '2017-03-28 16:42:50', 15, '0'),
(78, 27, '<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\">1.<span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: xx-small;\"><span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span></span><!--[endif]--><u><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif;\">border</span></span></u><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif;\"> Универсальное свойство border позволяет одновременно установить толщину, стиль и цвет границы вокруг элемента.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\">2.<span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: xx-small;\"><span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span class=\"apple-converted-space\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">&nbsp;</span></span></span><span class=\"attribute\"><u><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">margin</span></span></span></u></span><span class=\"apple-converted-space\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">позволяют задать величину отступа сразу для всех сторон </span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\">3.<span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: xx-small;\"><span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span></span><!--[endif]--><u><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif;\">Background</span></span></u><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif;\"> Универсальное свойство позволяет установить одновременно до пяти характеристик фона.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\">4.<span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: xx-small;\"><span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span></span><!--[endif]--><u><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif;\">box-shadow</span></span></u><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif;\"> Добавляет тень к элементу. Допускается использовать несколько теней, указывая их параметры через запятую,</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\">5.<span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: xx-small;\"><span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span></span><!--[endif]--><u><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif;\">background-repeat</span></span></u><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif;\"> Определяет, как будет повторяться фоновое изображение, установленное с помощью свойства background-image. </span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\">6.<span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: xx-small;\"><span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span></span><!--[endif]--><u><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif;\">border-right-color</span></span></u><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif;\"> Задаёт цвет границы справа от элемента.</span></span></p>', 'https://www.dropbox.com/s/nvzdm6ar7w6n1ul/DZ_Lesson2_Alexey.zip?dl=0', 0, '2017-03-24 09:24:19', '2017-03-27 10:54:45', 16, '0'),
(79, 19, '<p>1. border</p>\r\n<p>2. padding</p>\r\n<p>3. background</p>\r\n<p>4. shadow</p>\r\n<p>5. background-repeat</p>\r\n<p>6. border-right-color</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; margin: 0px 0px 0.5rem; padding: 0px; color: #7f8c8d; line-height: 1.4; font-size: 1.6rem;\">Ошибки в тесте: вопросы №6,11,12,13,15.</h2>', 'https://www.dropbox.com/s/anotyrco9eqp4kv/dz.zip?dl=0', 0, '2017-03-24 11:49:41', '2017-03-27 15:52:19', 17, '0'),
